'''凌新生'''（{{bd|1964年|2月15日||}}）是一位美国华人物理学家，专攻于[[凝聚态物理学|凝聚态物理学]]和[[超导现象|超导现象]]。<ref name="auto">{{cite web|title=Xinsheng Ling|url=https://vivo.brown.edu/display/xling|website=Brown University|publisher=Brown University|access-date=28 March 2018|archive-date=2021-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210225113648/https://vivo.brown.edu/display/xling|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==生平 ==
1964年出生于[[湖北|湖北]][[武汉|武汉]]，1984年获得[[武汉大学|武汉大学]]物理系学士学位，1987年获得[[中国科学院大学|中国科学院大学]]金属研究所硕士学位，1992年获得[[康涅狄格大学|康涅狄格大学]]博士学位。<ref name="auto" />之后在[[耶鲁大学|耶鲁大学]]和NEC研究所进行博士后工作。1996年加入[[布朗大学|布朗大学]]担任教授。2004年和美国物理学家[[利昂·库珀|利昂·库珀]]创立美国首个纳米孔DNA测序技术公司NABsys, Inc，2015年在[[南京|南京]]创建罗岛纳米科技有限公司并担任董事长。2017年5月22日创建[[苏州大学高等研究院|苏州大学高等研究院]]并担任初代院长。

==荣誉==
1998年获得[[斯隆奖|斯隆奖]]，2002年获得[[古根海姆奖|古根海姆奖]]，2005年被选为[[美国物理学会|美国物理学会]]会士。<ref name="auto" /><ref>{{cite web |title=John Simon Guggenheim Memorial Foundation Fellowships |url=https://www.brown.edu/about/administration/dean-of-faculty/faculty-awards-and-honors/john-simon-guggenheim-memorial-foundation-fellowships |publisher=Brown University |access-date=2021-02-28 |archive-date=2019-07-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190705203941/https://www.brown.edu/about/administration/dean-of-faculty/faculty-awards-and-honors/john-simon-guggenheim-memorial-foundation-fellowships |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=American Physical Society Fellows |url=https://www.brown.edu/about/administration/dean-of-faculty/faculty-awards-and-honors/american-physical-society-fellows |publisher=Brown University |access-date=2021-02-28 |archive-date=2019-07-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190705203942/https://www.brown.edu/about/administration/dean-of-faculty/faculty-awards-and-honors/american-physical-society-fellows |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Sloan Research Fellows |url=https://sloan.org/past-fellows |publisher=Alfred P. Sloan Foundation |access-date=2021-02-28 |archive-date=2018-03-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180314000756/https://sloan.org/past-fellows |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=NABsys and Brown University Establish Strategic Partnership |url=https://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20050809005712/en/NABsys-Brown-University-Establish-Strategic-Partnership-Brown |website=Business Wire |date=2005-08-09 |access-date=2021-02-28 |archive-date=2019-05-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190526080725/https://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20050809005712/en/NABsys-Brown-University-Establish-Strategic-Partnership-Brown |dead-url=no }}</ref>

